snippet.title: Cardiac - A Surreal Unnerving Dream
snippet.description:
https://katanalevy.itch.io/cardiac

Slop your way through a strange and unsettling dream.

Everything was created from scratch in my free time over 6 weeks as a personal challenge instead of inktober this year. Full game available to download for free.
